00:05:20.870 --> 00:05:23.550
So who was Ernest Orlando Lawrence?

00:05:23.550 --> 00:05:26.430
Well the short answer is
that during his lifetime,

00:05:26.430 --> 00:05:31.200
he was the most famous native
born scientist in America.

00:05:31.200 --> 00:05:32.500
Thank you.

00:05:32.500 --> 00:05:38.070
