fame and influence.

00:06:20.440 --> 00:06:23.140
He would go on to play a
crucial role in the development

00:06:23.140 --> 00:06:26.120
of the atomic bomb
and the hydrogen bomb.

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:29.470
And we'll be talking a little
