00:06:40.450 --> 00:06:42.560
But Lawrence's overarching
legacy was

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:47.550 position:56%
that he created this new paradigm
of science that still prevails today

00:06:47.550 --> 00:06:49.450
and big science is all around us.

00:06:49.450 --> 00:06:53.960 position:56%
High level research funded by the
NIH, the National Science Foundation

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:56.990
which received nearly
$40 billion a year

00:06:56.990 --> 00:07:00.480
and government appropriations,
well that's big science.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:04.390
Masses effort to put a man on
the moon and to send probes

00:07:04.390 --> 00:07:08.790
into the farthest reaches of the
solar system, that's big science.

00:07:08.790 --> 00:07:14.160
The human genome project was a $3
billion exercise in big science

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:18.540
that launched not only new fields
of study, but new industries.

00:07:18.540 --> 00:07:24.490
Solving climate change will be
impossible without big science.

00:07:24.490 --> 00:07:27.650
The Large Hadron Collider,
which discovered

00:07:27.650 --> 00:07:32.450
that illusive subatomic particle,
the Higgs Boson in 2012, well,

00:07:32.450 --> 00:07:35.310
that's the latest iteration
of the first cyclotron

00:07:35.310 --> 00:07:39.710
that Ernest Lawrence invented
more than eight decades ago.

00:07:39.710 --> 00:07:44.660
That first cyclotron cost less
than a $100 in materials and is fit

00:07:44.660 --> 00:07:47.070
in the palm of this hand.

00:07:47.070 --> 00:07:50.750
It's offspring today, it
occupies a tunnel 17 miles

00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:55.000
in circumference buried under
the French in Swiss countrysides

00:07:55.000 --> 00:08:01.300
and it cost $9 billion, and
the cost is still rising.

00:08:01.300 --> 00:08:08.510
In fact, here's an illustration
of the cyclotron's phenology.

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:12.750
And one of Lawrence's very first
devices is there on the left.

00:08:12.750 --> 00:08:14.050
It's a small container.

00:08:14.050 --> 00:08:16.290
It's lathered with red sealing wax

00:08:16.290 --> 00:08:21.460
to keep the vacuum
