00:09:06.500 --> 00:09:11.180
Yet for all that, one central theme
of my book is that this paradigm

00:09:11.180 --> 00:09:14.050
that Lawrence pioneered
raises as many questions

00:09:14.050 --> 00:09:18.060
about human kind search for
knowledge as an answers.

00:09:18.060 --> 00:09:21.400
One of the most important
aspects of big science

00:09:21.400 --> 00:09:25.200
that we're still grappling
