00:09:29.220 --> 00:09:32.220
forces that we found
very hard and we hope

00:09:32.220 --> 00:09:36.230
in the long run not
impossible to control.

00:09:36.230 --> 00:09:37.900
Among the first people to warn

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:40.870
of the implications was
Lawrence's own colleague

00:09:40.870 --> 00:09:44.130
on the Manhattan project,
James Franck, a German

00:09:44.130 --> 00:09:48.320
and a great physicist who two
